jjil.j2se.ocr
Class JessRect

java.lang.Object
  jjil.core.Rect
      jjil.j2se.ocr.JessRect

public class JessRect
extends jjil.core.Rect

Tesseract uses a coordinate system where left and right are reversed relative to JJIL. The origin is the bottom left corner of the page, x increasing to the right and y increasing upwards. So the top left corner has minimum x coordinate and maximum y coordinate.
